      	 Connect suggestion to add included columns to sp_helpindex 
       				 Leave a comment 
		         January 10, 2017  by Kenneth Fisher 

		 
			 I’m a big fan of the  sp_help system stored procedures , which is why I’ve been a bit disappointed that the  sp_helpindex  stored procedure is rather badly flawed.  It doesn’t have the included columns from the index.  This seems a bit strange to me since included columns first appeared in SQL 2005 (&gt;10 years ago) and are very important when doing index ana